        <h1>Aoede (ay-EE-dee) - Language Study Reinvented</h1>
        <p>Experience a revolutionary way to learn languages through reading, and <em>listening</em>, practice</p>
        
        <div class="features">
            <h2>Key Features:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>To get started with Aoede, select the language you want to study, your desired reading level (from beginner to advanced), and any of dozens of classic literary choices. Then click Load Book to see the first sentence, simplified according to your selected reading level. Click Next Sentence to proceed onto the next sentence.</li>
                <li>Aoede allows you to view each sentence in your study language, or your own language, or both. You can even practice listening for comprehension without seeing the sentence at all if you wish.</li>
                <li>You can adjust Aoede's reading speed from slow to fast to practice listening at your own desired speed.</li>
                <li>Aoede's Listen button plays each foreign sentence with the simulated voice of a native speaker.</li>
                <li>Aoede remembers where you are in each book, even across sessions.</li>
                <li>Aoede automatically displays in your own language.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
